<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>정부대전청사공무원노조연합회 전용 페이지</title>
<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #f2f2f2;
        display: flex;
        height: 100vh;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin: 0;
    }
    .box {
        background: white;
        padding: 35px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        text-align: center;
        width: 320px;
    }
    h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 18px;
    }
    input {
        padding: 12px;
        width: 220px;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
    }
    button {
        margin-top: 15px;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
        cursor: pointer;
        background: #1a73e8;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }
    button:hover {
        background: #155fc0;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="box">
    <h2>정부대전청사공무원노조연합회<br>비밀번호를 입력하시오.</h2>

    <input type="password" id="pw" placeholder="비밀번호 입력">
    <br>
    <button onclick="checkPw()">입력</button>
</div>

<script>
function checkPw() {
    const pw = document.getElementById("pw").value;

    if (pw === "1234") {
        location.href = "https://naver.me/xcnavVEs";
    } else {
        alert("비밀번호가 틀렸습니다.");
    }
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
